### Box Component: Basic Usage and Rendering

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Shows the fundamental usage of the Box component for layout in Ink applications. It's analogous to a flex container in web development and includes an example of rendering a Box with margin.

```jsx
import {render, Box, Text} from 'ink';

const Example = () => (
	<Box margin={2}>
		<Text>This is a box with margin</Text>
	</Box>
);

render(<Example />);
```

