### Box Component: Height

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Illustrates setting the height of a Box component. Height can be specified in absolute units (lines) or as a percentage of the parent element's height.

```jsx
<Box height={4}>
	<Text>X</Text>
</Box>
//=> 'X\n\n\n'
```

```jsx
<Box height={6} flexDirection="column">
	<Box height="50%">
		<Text>X</Text>
	</Box>
	<Text>Y</Text>
</Box>
//=> 'X\n\n\nY\n\n'
```

