### Render React Component to Terminal with render()

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Core API for mounting and rendering a React component to the terminal. Accepts a ReactElement tree and optional configuration object. Returns an Instance object for managing the rendered app. Supports custom stdout, stdin, stderr streams and Ctrl+C handling.

```javascript
import {render} from 'ink';

// Basic usage
render(<App />);

// With options
render(<App />, {
	stdout: process.stdout,
	stdin: process.stdin,
	stderr: process.stderr,
	exitOnCtrlC: true
});
```

