### Replace Root Node with rerender

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Illustrates replacing the entire root node with a new component using the rerender method. This is useful when the structure or type of the main component needs to change.

```jsx
import {render} from 'ink';

// Assume OldCounter and NewCounter are components
const {rerender} = render(<OldCounter />);
rerender(<NewCounter />);
```

