### Box Component: Width

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Demonstrates setting the width of a Box component. Width can be specified in absolute units (spaces) or as a percentage of the parent element's width.

```jsx
<Box width={4}>
	<Text>X</Text>
</Box>
//=> 'X   '
```

```jsx
<Box width={10}>
	<Box width="50%">
		<Text>X</Text>
	</Box>
	<Text>Y</Text>
