### Basic Ink App with Text Component

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

A minimal Ink application demonstrating the rendering of a 'Hello World' message using the `<Text>` component. This serves as a fundamental example of Ink's structure.

```jsx
import React from 'react';
import {render, Text} from 'ink';

const Demo = () => <Text>Hello World</Text>;

render(<Demo />);
```

