### Update Root Node Props with rerender

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Demonstrates how to update the properties of the current root node using the rerender method. This is useful for modifying existing components without replacing them entirely.

```jsx
import {render} from 'ink';

// Assume Counter is a component that takes a 'count' prop
const {rerender} = render(<Counter count={1} />);
rerender(<Counter count={2} />);
```
